syso + ctrl+spacebar = System.out.println();
main+ctrl+spacebar = public static void main (String[]args){}
for single line comment=  ctrl+/
for single line uncomment= ctrl+/
for multiline comment= ctrl+shift+/
for multiline uncomment= ctrl+shift+\
code formatting = ctrl+shift+f
To search target file(.class file) = ctrl+shift+T
To search Resource file(.java file) =ctrl+shift+R
ctrl+D = To delete selected content.
ctrl+shift+w = to clear all open class tab.
